overview.en: A multi-cryptocurrencies preservation and payment wallet with enhancement of smart contract control. It supports mainstream cryptocurrencies such as ETH, EOS, BCH, the advanced control of smart contract and tokens.
overview.zh: 链宝智能钱包,一款数字资产的保存和支付工具，强化支持智能合约操控的多币种智能钱包。支持 ETH，EOS，BTC, BCH 等主要基础货币，对智能合约 DAPP 全面支持。
